  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group Study to Evaluate the Benefit of a Probiotic (Bifidobacterium Infantis 35624) in Healthy Subjects With a History of Abdominal Discomfort and Bloating</official_title>
